The paper investigates the uplink of multi-user massive MIMO systems with a mixed ADC receiver architecture, which involves signal processing, communication theory, and hardware design. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), which deals with the fundamental limits of data communication and storage. The paper also involves networked systems (cs.NI), control and optimization (cs.SY), signal processing (cs.MM), and architecture (cs.AR) aspects, which are relevant to the design and implementation of communication systems.
